services:
AGM Renovations offers Complete basement and Bathroom renovations packages from the professional design through the professional cleaning including:

Drywall- We employ only professional drywall installers and our goal is deliver complete satisfaction to each and every client with the quality of our workmanship and our prompt, reliable service.
    
Taping- Our drywall taping techniques will bring a high quality smooth finish, with a level of excellence you will take pride in.

Painting- We include all wall priming, painting of ceilings, baseboards, casing, crown and cove moldings into our basement construction packages
    
High Grade Laminate Flooring- is standard in our basement renovations packages.

Tiling- Shower, bathroom, or kitchenette tiling will be done by professional tile installers who are employed directly by AGM. A 2 year unlimited warranty is provided to you standard when you finish your basement with AGM
   
Plumbing- Our licensed plumbers will ensure that no problem is left unsolved and you can be sure that any drain or other plumbing defects left by the original house builder will be fixed effectively.

Electrical- We are committed to providing fully licensed electrician service as part of our standard package. Should you ever require an electrical certificate when you decide to sell your property, we will be happy to provide it to you

Techno Kitchen Refacing is an Ontario based kitchen renovation company that specializes in refacing, rather than replacing. Recently, we brought on another member to the team to supply the increasing demand. Now, we can serve you faster, and across a larger area.

Techno's word-of-mouth marketing philosophy shows how happy customers have been with the product. Honesty and customer satisfaction are of the utmost concern for Techno and the customer will benefit every time.

Want to see it for yourself? Our customers are so happy and enthusiastic about the work that they've allowed us to invite you into their homes to see firsthand the quality of the work. Call today and ask how to arrange a meeting with Frank.

Why Choose Techno?
Full Satisfaction Guarantee! Real wood doors and veneer in several different stains, colors and species! No plastic, no paper, no cheap looking laminate! We're a member of the Better Business Bureau! You work directly with the owner who will be personally involved in making your dream kitchen a reality!
services: Cabinet repainting, cabinet refacing and custom-built cabinetry and entertainment units.
specialities:
*WE SPECIALIZE IN REAL WOOD*
After 15 years of experience in the woodworking and cabinetry industry, Techno founder Frank Silletti chose to start his own refacing company with the goal of giving homeowners in Ontario a more affordable alternative to traditional kitchen remodeling. Frank says "By using the cabinet refacing process, we are able to dramatically cut down the time, cost and inconvenience of building and creating your dream kitchen". With the experience and the motivation to back his work, you can be sure Frank will be there to answer any questions or concerns to deliver the best value and quality of work available. Please feel free to visit the contact page and fill out an information request form. We look forward to hearing from you!

Your home is where your family makes memories to last a life time; make sure it’s the backdrop you have always envisioned. Our team has what it takes to bring your vision to life.  Whether you are hoping for a simple refresh of a bathroom, adding better functionality to your kitchen space, or transforming your main floor into your dream oasis, Edge Kitchens has the skills and professional know-how to bring it all together.
  
Edge Kitchens is family owned and operated custom kitchen and bathroom renovation company in Oakville, ON.  Our team brings over 20+ years of experience in home renovations.  We strive to exceed our Customer’s expectations from the initial consult, design, and installation to ensure a positive experience and successful job. Let us design your dream space and see what all the fuss is about – you won’t be disappointed!

- Professional installation
............................

profile:
Welcome to Ritchie Custom Cabinetry
Ritchie Custom Cabinetry, established in 1995 is your "One Stop" Custom built cabinet shop. 

WE ARE CABINET MAKERS
We aren’t big and proud of it! That’s right, we pride ourselves on being an alternative to the big box stores. Since 1993 we have spent our lives building a business we are proud of. We love what we do and it shows.

Ritchie Custom Cabinetry is a family affair established and run by Ken and Jennifer Ritchie. Ken is a professional cabinet maker with years of experience building fine cabinets but also knows everything there needs to known about the custom cabinet business. That business includes managing an entire project from design to install, working with clients to get the best product for their budget, anticipating problems and solving issues that are unique with each project, coordinating and managing sub contractors so projects run smoothly and on time…its a big job.

Jennifer, Ken’s wife and business partner, knows design and has a keen eye for making an ordinary project special. Jennifer knows design trends and is excellent at helping clients find the style and design best suited for them. From deciding on paint colours, accessories and all aspects of the project details, Jennifer and Ken make a powerful team.

With their skilled and passionate team Ritchie Custom Cabinetry delivers a great product that will last for years looking great and functioning like new.
We will walk you through the entire process of Designing,Style,and Colour choice,to make the Dream Cabinetry you are looking for. 
We manufacture ALL of the cabinetry and can deliver and install generally in 4-6 weeks. 
A 3D design is offered for each job to let you truly picture your new cabinetry. 

Visit our New Modern showroom to discuss your next project!

profile:
At Azule Kitchens we understand that your kitchen is the heart of your home and that no two kitchens are the same. We work hard to bring our customers a product that is tailored to their unique individual needs at an affordable price. We provide complete solutions for all your cabinetry needs, from innovative trends to classic traditional cuisine. We provide only the highest quality Canadian made cabinetry at an affordable price combined with the highest level of customer service and customer care. We understand how important it is to have a company that works with you, listens to your needs and wants and stands with you every step of the way. We have only the most qualified and experienced designers that work with you from concept to completion to ensure you get nothing less than your dream kitchen. Azule kitchens is a family owned and operated company. 
 
Based in Stoney Creek, Ontario. We provide complete solutions for all your cabinetry needs; kitchen, bath, basement and whole home cabinetry to surrounding areas including: Stoney Creek, Oakville, Burlington, Hamilton, Ancaster, Grimsby, Beamsville, St Catharines, Mississauga, Toronto, Brantford, Kitchener, Cambridge, Guelph and Waterloo. Please explore our site and contact us for a no-obligation consultation.
 
We invite you to visit us in our showroom at:
442 Millen Road Unit 117
Stoney Creek, ON L8E 6H2
 
or email us: info@azulekitchens.ca
 
or call us: 905-664-1112
